rdf:Property.rdfs:comment: This property identifies the E24 Physical Human-Made Thing that came into existence as a result of an E12 Production. The identity of an instance of E24 Physical Human-Made Thing is not defined by its matter, but by its existence as a subject of documentation. An E12 Production can result in the creation of multiple instances of E24 Physical Human-Made Thing.
